<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Cache-Control Demo</title>
  </head>

  <body>

    Path format:
    <ol>
      <li>no_revalidate | must_revalidate | no-cache | no-store</li>
      <li>no_last_modified | same_last_modified | different_last_modified</li>
      <li>no_etag | same_etag | different_etag</li>
    </ol>
    Options:
    <ul>
      <li>age (the current age as estimated by the server)</li>
      <li>max (will be set as the max-age)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @request_url %>"><%= @request_url %></a>
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= Time.now.to_i.to_s %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
